OL,4,Cfootball star backs road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FOne of the stars of the Northern
OL,8,FIreland football team is backing a new
OL,9,Froad safety campaign.
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland international and
OL,12,FLiverpool FC defender Conor Bradley
OL,13,Fhas put his name to the Department for
OL,14,FInfrastructure's Share The Road To
OL,15,FZero initiative.
OL,17,FIt comes after 71 people died on the
OL,18,Fregion's roads in 2023, up from 55 in
OL,19,F2022 and 50 in 2021.
