OL,4,Cfootball star backs road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of Northern Ireland's
OL,8,FNations League match against Bulgaria
OL,9,Fon Sunday evening, the 21-year-old
OL,10,Fplayer said he is aware of how
OL,11,Fdevastating crashes can be, and hopes
OL,12,Fto spread the road safety message to
OL,13,Fyoung people.
OL,15,F"More than one quarter of all speeding
OL,16,Foffences last year involved young
OL,17,Fdrivers and, as a young person, that
OL,18,Fis a message I would like to share,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
