OL,7,F"By signing up to the campaign I hope
OL,8,Fto remind others to be more careful on
OL,9,Fthe roads, watch their speed and stay
OL,10,Foff their phones."
OL,12,FThe Irish Football Association (IFA),
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Football League,
OL,14,FUlster GAA, PSNI, Northern Ireland
OL,15,FAmbulance Service, Northern Ireland
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service, Sustrans NI
OL,17,Fand councils have also backed the
OL,18,Fcampaign.
