OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister John O'Dowd
OL,8,Fsaid one of the best ways to ensure
OL,9,Fsafety on the roads and eliminate
OL,10,Fdeath and serious injury by 2050 is by
OL,11,Fchanging road user behaviour.
OL,13,F"We all have a personal responsibility
OL,14,Fto behave in a way that keeps
OL,15,Fourselves and others safe, and my
OL,16,Fdepartment's Share The Road To Zero
OL,17,Fcampaign reminds us of that," he said.
