OL,3,CNorthern Ireland and Liverpool
OL,4,Cfootball star backs road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,F"The sad reality is that, if we do not
OL,8,Fchange our own attitudes when we are
OL,9,Fusing the roads, our death toll will
OL,10,Fcontinue to increase.
OL,12,F"I am delighted to have the IFA and
OL,13,FConor sign up to the pledge and would
OL,14,Fencourage others to follow in their
OL,15,Ffootsteps and help us all Share The
OL,16,FRoad To Zero."
OL,18,FIFA president Conrad Kirkwood said:
OL,19,F"Sadly the number of people who have
OL,20,Flost their lives on the roads has
OL,21,Frisen.
